import concatArrays from './5-spread-operator.js';

console.log(concatArrays(['a', 'b'], ['c', 'd'], 'Hello'));
export function concatArrays(array1, array2, string) { return ([...array1, ...array2, ...string]); }
export default function concatArrays(array1, array2, string) { return ([...array1, ...array2, ...string]); }
